===[[Pokémon Masters EX]]===
{{main|Lysandre (Masters)}}
Lysandre forms a [[sync pair]] with {{p|Yveltal}} and {{p|Volcanion}} in [[Pokémon Masters EX]]. Lysandre became a playable sync pair on February 11, 2021.

Lysandre has also made notable appearances in the game's main stories, [[Legendary Adventures]] and the [[villain arc]].

